# Ignore everything
*

# Keep tracked essentials
!.gitignore
!README
!README.md
!CHANGELOG.md
!L1-L10-matrix-simple.md
!claude-code-memory-and-settings-hierarchy.md

# Keep lesson books and indexes
!COURSE-INDEX.md
!2_lessons/
!2_lessons/*.md
!2_lessons/codex-book/
!2_lessons/codex-book/*.md
!2_lessons/claude-code-book/
!2_lessons/claude-code-book/*.md
!2_lessons/playbooks/
!2_lessons/playbooks/*.md

# Keep framework memory docs
!.claude/
!.claude/SNAPSHOT.md
!.claude/BACKLOG.md
!.claude/ARCHITECTURE.md
!.claude/ROADMAP.md
!.claude/IDEAS.md
!.claude/SESSION-HANDOFF.md

# Always ignore local Finder artifacts
.DS_Store

# Claude Code local permissions and local credential bundles must never be committed
.claude/settings.local.json
.production-credentials

.env
.env.*
*credentials*
*.pem
*.key
.claude/.last_session
.claude/.session-owner
.claude/logs/
reports/
